name: Flag of Vietnam
description: Vietnam is a country in Southeast Asia. This flag of Vietnam were built and maintained by r/placevietnam. It features a yellow five-pointed star on a red background. This was the old location of the Vietnam flag at the start of the event, until it got captured by Portugal around 23:00 GMT on July 20. Afterward, r/placevietnam move to a new location (next to Osu).
